articles.title: Woman who suffered 80% burns trying to save fiance in Tanjong Pagar crash in positive spirits since discharge - The Star Online
articles.description: SINGAPORE (The Straits Times/Asia News Network): After about four months in hospital, Raybe Oh Siew Huey, the 26-year-old who suffered serious burns attempting to save her fiance from a burning car, was discharged in June.
